# Black & Yellow Theme â€” Consistent Design Across All Pages

Apply a unified **black & yellow** color scheme across the entire admin frontend using **Roboto** and **Poppins** fonts, driven from [globals.css](file:///d:/mix-studio-org/haannaa/admin-frontend/app/globals.css) CSS variables. Content and logic stay unchanged â€” only colors, fonts, and typography tokens change.

## Design System

| Token | Value | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `--background` | `#0a0a0a` | Main page background |
| `--foreground` | `#f5f5f5` | Primary text |
| `--card` | `#111111` | Card/panel backgrounds |
| `--primary` | `#F5C518` (yellow) | CTAs, active states, accents |
| `--primary-foreground` | `#0a0a0a` | Text on yellow buttons |
| `--secondary` | `#1a1a1a` | Secondary surfaces |
| `--muted` | `#1c1c1c` | Input backgrounds, muted areas |
| `--muted-foreground` | `#888` | Dimmed text |
| `--border` | `#2a2a2a` | All borders |
| `--sidebar` | `#0f0f0f` | Sidebar background |
| Fonts | Roboto (body) + Poppins (headings) | Via Google Fonts |

