### Global Styles & Fonts

#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///d:/mix-studio-org/haannaa/admin-frontend/app/globals.css)
- Update all CSS variable values in `:root` and `.dark` to black & yellow palette
- Replace glassmorphism utilities to use yellow accent colors
- Add `--font-sans` (Roboto) and `--font-heading` (Poppins) font variables
- Apply consistent base body/html font rules in `@layer base`

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///d:/mix-studio-org/haannaa/admin-frontend/app/layout.tsx)
